<bibRefCitation id="46174B6ACB2BFFC3FD3C66AD301655FF" author="Mutin" box="[756,1039,1458,1483]" pageId="4" pageNumber="289" refString="Mutin, V. A. &amp; Barkalov, A. V. (1999) 62. Family Syrphidae. In: Lehr, P. A. (Ed.), Key to the insects of Russian Far East. Vol. 6. Diptera and Siphonaptera. Part 1. Dal'nauka, Valdivostok, pp. 342 - 500. [in Russian]" type="book chapter" year="1999">
